==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prognostication
<hw>Prog*nos`ti*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>prognostication</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of foreshowing or foretelling something
future by present signs; prediction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which foreshows; a foretoken.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prognosticator</ent>⟦br⟧
